3. **Verify CoLA MCC metric:** Check training code to confirm whether `eval/matthews_correlation` stores actual MCC or accuracy. If accuracy, add proper MCC computation.

4. **Investigate STS-B seed 46:** The anomalous final eval/pearson (0.556) may indicate a corrupted evaluation. Re-run or use second-to-last evaluation.

